{"word":"σχίσμα","slug":"σχίσμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>σχίσμα, ατος, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σχίζω\">σχίζω</a></el>] ‘<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> that is in parts through force’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of fabric <b><a href='B:470 9:16'>Mt 9:16</a>; <a href='B:480 2:21'>Mk 2:21</a>;</b> of the human body <b><a href='B:530 12:25'>1 Cor 12:25</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ metaph.\">metaph.</a> application following in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vss.\">vss.</a> 27–31; others put <b><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vs.\">vs.</a> 25</b>in b)<b>.</b> By metonymy<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of a group of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> with difference in viewpoint<b> <a href='B:500 7:43'>J 7:43</a>; <a href='B:500 9:16'>9:16</a>; <a href='B:500 10:19'>10:19</a>; <a href='B:530 1:10'>1 Cor 1:10</a>; <a href='B:530 11:18'>11:18</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ perh.\">perh.</a> <b><a href='B:530 12:25'>12:25</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σχίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σχοινίον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}